      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a name=\"overview\"&gt;</ph><ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>Feature description"
    },
    {
      "content": "The <ph id=\"ph1\">[!INCLUDE[ise_2](../Token/ise_2_md.md)]</ph> is a host application that enables you to write, run, and test scripts and modules in a graphical and intuitive environment.",
      "pos": [
